      <item>
        <title>Return 404 status for 404 pages</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[SantosGuillamot]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Yes, maybe we can add a tag <code>status: closed</code> for the topics that doesn’t make sense anymore like this one and keep using the <code>status:release</code> for the features that are released.</p>
<p>I’m planning to show the status tag in a clearer way, and it should help to identify that the topic is closed. Something like this:</p>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/1X/e6196db76e8f42f3e9c37115189ebe63ded29100.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/e6196db76e8f42f3e9c37115189ebe63ded29100" title="Screenshot 2020-01-28 at 13.04.34"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/1X/e6196db76e8f42f3e9c37115189ebe63ded29100_2_675x500.png" alt="Screenshot 2020-01-28 at 13.04.34" data-base62-sha1="wPyiw91kyDkXLxmC4FopD8QYE36" width="675" height="500" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/1X/e6196db76e8f42f3e9c37115189ebe63ded29100_2_675x500.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/1X/e6196db76e8f42f3e9c37115189ebe63ded29100.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/1X/e6196db76e8f42f3e9c37115189ebe63ded29100.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/1X/e6196db76e8f42f3e9c37115189ebe63ded29100_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>Do you think that would be enough?</p>
<p>Regarding the votes, I agree we could allow them to vote as many topics as they want, there is no problem about that.</p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/return-404-status-for-404-pages/1011/7">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
